title: Blacked - Natasha Nice, Kylie Page (Two curvy girls compete) NEW
description:
Kylie and Natasha are both going up for a part in an up and coming music video. They are the last two girls left after a series of auditions and they are just what the producer is looking for. Unfortunately, there is only one part left and he decides to interview both the girls to decide which is the right one for the job. After he takes a long time interviewing Kylie, Natasha decides she will check on them. Unsurprisingly, when Natasha walks into the room, Kylie is doing more than is required to get the job. Both girls are eager and willing to do whatever is required to get the part, even if that means teaming up together.
